OL,3,CCommissioners recommend handing back
OL,4,Ccontrol to Liverpool Council
OL,6,FCommissioners brought in to run parts
OL,7,Fof after allegations of corruption
OL,8,Fhave recommended that some powers be
OL,9,Fhanded back to the authority.
OL,11,FBut the eagerly-awaited move after
OL,12,Fnearly three years came with a caveat
OL,13,Fthat some oversight should continue.
OL,15,FThe Government after an inspection was
OL,16,Fordered in December 2020 following the
OL,17,Farrests of a number of people.
