OL,6,FCouncil leader Liam Robinson, who took
OL,7,Fup his post in May 2023 after the role
OL,8,Fof elected mayor was abolished, said:
OL,9,F"Nobody ever wanted commissioner
OL,10,Fintervention, but as soon as that
OL,11,Fhappened, it was incumbent on us to
OL,12,Fwork very, very closely with the
OL,13,Fcommissioners, to have the right
OL,14,Fprofessional, working relationship, to
OL,15,Fwork our way through this improvement
OL,16,Fjourney that's got us to this point
OL,17,Ftoday.
