OL,6,FThe Department of Levelling Up,
OL,7,FHousing and Communities has said
OL,8,FSecretary of State Michael Gove is
OL,9,Fminded to extend the intervention by
OL,10,Fappointing an statutory assurance and
OL,11,Fimprovement board and has asked for
OL,12,Frepresentations before a final
OL,13,Fdecision is made.
OL,15,FThirteen people have been arrested and
OL,16,Freleased under investigation as part
OL,17,Fof Operation Aloft, the police probe
OL,18,Finto alleged fraud involving the
OL,19,Fcouncil.
